{"tid":1052711,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【愛子般的彭健新離世4年】OK仔與妻相依相靠 孖公仔買餸煮飯仔","createTime":"2019-03-08T13:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T12:03:29.000Z","uid":1121,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc410bfc73614912fbcef0b10b0b3aa9e956d4c","tid":1052711,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:19:37.000Z","msg":"講起OK仔，大家首先諗起咩？話唔定彭健新呢個答案，仲多過溫拿。無計啦，以前OK仔無論去邊都會帶埋愛犬彭健新，連工作上節目都唔例外，例如OK仔連《美女廚房》都上過呀！有兩大美女楊恭如、廖碧兒煮畀佢食都唔吼，相當好笑。難怪有段時間，啲人講笑話其實啲節目主要係請OK仔，彭健新只係附帶嘉賓。有啲人仲搞笑，甚至會叫錯彭健新做OK仔。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，彭健新已經離開咗差唔多4年喇！無彭健新陪伴嘅呢段日子，好彩仲有老婆做伴，不時孖公仔外出過二人世界，有時又會好似呢日咁一齊去買餸當拍拖，然後兩公婆返屋企匿埋玩煮飯仔。見佢兩公婆各自拎住袋餸現身，望真啲，兩大袋都係菜，食得咁健康，難怪兩公婆手腳都咁纖幼啦。之後佢哋入咗間相熟餐廳，吹咗陣水，出嚟之後老婆手上多咗盒疑似外賣，斷估都係斬料加餸。兩口子嚟計，食得幾豐富喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_657808_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3XLIpZg_WQ9Ny-OAbRdaRwjt7Mi1KYadrZu1oQkvt1gsvFzxh2PQ6GzTA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_657808_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3XLIpZg_WQ9Ny-OAbRdaRwjt7Mi1KYadrZu1oQkvt1gsvFzxh2PQ6GzTA&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMpMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=d8c2bf98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_657808_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3XLIpZg_WQ9Ny-OAbRdaRwjt7Mi1KYadrZu1oQkvt1gsvFzxh2PQ6GzTA&h=fa101aec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_657808_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3XLIpZg_WQ9Ny-OAbRdaRwjt7Mi1KYadrZu1oQkvt1gsvFzxh2PQ6GzTA</a>"},{"pid":"250e38afe2d7e65fc4c72